  <locationDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel Derby is opposite the train station, and a short walk to the main street where you can find a range of shops, cafes and restaurants (approx. 100 metres).</p>
<p>The resort bus stop is 50 metres from the hotel.</p>
<p>The Grindelwald terminal is around 1.4 kilometres away, accessible by bus.</p>
<p>Access to the First Mountain is approximately 900 metres walk.</p>
<p>The Bodmi beginner area is accessible by the resort bus.</p>]]></locationDescription>
